# 1. Project Overview

| Category           | Details                                                                                   |
|--------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Purpose**        | All-in-one coding platform for interview prep, competitive programming, and skill development |
| **Target Audience**| CS students, self-taught developers, coding competition participants                     |
| **Key Objectives** | Democratize interview prep, provide structured learning, bridge theory/practice          |
| **Unique Value**   | AI mentor, company-specific problems, video explanations                                 |

---

# 2. Core Features

## User-Facing Features

| Feature                  | Description                                                    | Icon |
