## Admin-Facing Features

| Feature            | Description                                 |
|--------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| User Management    | View/edit user roles and activity logs       |
| Platform Analytics | DAU, retention rates, problem completion     |
| Content Management | Create/edit problems and video explanations  |
| Community Moderation | Monitor discussions and flag content       |

---

# 3. AI Mentor System

## Capabilities

1. **Conceptual Scaffolding**
    - Identifies knowledge gaps
    - Provides relevant academic references
    - Links to similar problems

2. **Progressive Hint System**
    - Broad conceptual nudges â†’ specific guidance
    - Example: "Consider hash maps for O(1) lookups"

3. **Code Explanation Engine**
    - Explains selected code in plain English
    - Analyzes time/space complexity

## Technical Implementation

| Component         | Technology Used                  |
|-------------------|----------------------------------|
| Natural Language  | OpenAI GPT-4 with custom fine-tuning |
| Context Management| MongoDB conversation trees        |
| Rate Limiting     | Redis for API request throttling  |

---

# 4. Technology Stack

## Frontend

| Technology   | Purpose         | Docs                                   |
|--------------|-----------------|----------------------------------------|
| React 18     | UI Components   | [React](https://react.dev/)            |
| TypeScript   | Type Safety     | [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/) |
| Redux Toolkit| State Management| [Redux Toolkit](https://redux-toolkit.js.org/) |

## Backend

| Technology | Purpose                 |
|------------|------------------------|
| Node.js    | Runtime Environment    |
| Express    | API Framework          |
| MongoDB    | NoSQL Database         |
| Socket.IO  | Real-time Communication|

---

# 5. Challenges & Solutions

| Challenge                | Solution                                                      |
|--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| Secure Code Execution    | Judge0 + Docker containers with read-only FS                 |
| Real-time Collaboration  | Socket.IO with Redis adapter and Operational Transform        |
| AI Context Management    | Vector embeddings + MongoDB conversation trees               |

---

# 6. Appendix

## A. Glossary

- **DAU**: Daily Active Users  
- **FAANG+**: Facebook, Apple, Amazon, Netflix, Google + similar tech companies

